%hive
create table if not  exists population (rank INT,state STRING,
pop BIGINT,growth DOUBLE,pop18 BIGINT,pop10 BIGINT,growth10 DOUBLE,perc DOUBLE,density DOUBLE)
COMMENT 'Population Table'
row format SERDE 'org.apache.hadoop.hive.serde2.OpenCSVSerde'
WITH SERDEPROPERTIES (
   "separatorChar" = "\,",
   "quoteChar"     = "\""
)
stored as textfile
LOCATION '/user/hive/warehouse/crimes.db/population'
tblproperties ('skip.header.line.count'='1')

paragraphs.title: Number of People Killed in US by state
paragraphs.text:
%hive
	select state, sum(n_killed) as killed
	from 
		gun_crime
	where
		n_killed>0
	group by
			state
	having
		killed>500
	order by
		killed desc
	limit 10

%hive
	select a.state, sum(a.n_killed) as killed, b.pop/10000 as popul, sum(a.n_killed)*10000000/b.pop as killedPer1000 
	from 
		gun_crime a join population b
	on (a.state = b.state)
	where
		a.n_killed>0
	group by
			a.state,b.pop
	having
		killed>500
	order by
		killed desc
	limit 10

paragraphs.title: No of People killed in Texas
paragraphs.text:
%hive
select state, city_or_county as place, year(crime_date) as dt, sum(n_killed) as killed
	from 
		gun_crime
	where
		n_killed>0
	and
	    state in ('Texas')
	group by
			state, city_or_county,year(crime_date)
	having
        killed >100
	order by
		killed desc
